  "selectedTrack": "windows-x64-aionui-relay-officecli",
  "ownershipBoundary": "Relay-branded AionUi owns UX, conversations, workspace files, skills, approvals, OfficeCLI assistants, previews, and lightweight Workspace Document Search result presentation. Relay owns the local OpenAI-compatible M365 Copilot provider gateway, tool-call emulation, diagnostics, user-local portable tool bootstrap, AionUi seed/bridge contracts, status translation, and evidence validation boundaries.",
